Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:48.83,Crime Edge,,0000,0000,0000,,Mushanokouji Iwai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:49.45,Crime Edge,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai người.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.93,Crime Edge,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghê thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:17.01,Crime Edge,,0000,0000,0000,,Là bọn chúng sao?
